name: Google Code Jam
caption: code.google.com
description: Now eleven years strong, the infamous Google Code Jam returns to throw intense algorithmic puzzles at programmers from around the world. Of the 45,000+ coders who registered to compete last year, it was Ivan Miatselski (mystic) of Belarus who, at the end of it all, stood alone as the Code Jam Champi...

data.message: This is a contest conducted by Google every year, & the qualification round is about to end in 2 hours, It contains 4 problems & you have to score at least 25 points (solving the first, easy, two problems is enough) to get to the next stage.
